# ðŸ”¥ **Slide 7 â€” Tech Stack (Decision Engine + Data Layer)**

### Underwriting Logic (Rule Matrix)

| Condition                      | Action                                           |
| ------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------ |
| Loan â‰¤ Preapproved Limit       | **Instant Approval**                             |
| Loan â‰¤ 2Ã— Limit                | Ask **Salary Slip** â†’ FOIR check â‰¤ 50% â†’ Approve |
| Loan > 2Ã— Limit OR Score < 700 | **Reject with reasoning**                        |

### FOIR Calculation

```
FOIR = (Existing EMI + New EMI) / Monthly Income Ã— 100
```

